{{wikipedia}}
==English==
===Noun===
'''[[Euclidean]] [[geometry]]''' {{uncountable}}

#{{geometry}} The [[familiar]] geometry of the [[real world]], based on the [[postulate]] that through any two [[point]]s there is exactly one [[straight line]].

